line_1: In Birds, as well as mortal Folks;
You send me such ill-coupled folks,
line_2: That 'tis a shame to sell them yokes.

line_1: They forc'd their way through draggled folks,
line_2: Who gap'd to catch Jack-Pudding's jokes.
To burn their nits, an' pou their stocks,

line_1: That PATRIOTS now, like other folks,
line_2: Were made the butt of vulgar jokes;
